<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>تَفْسِيرُ الْقُرْآن<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[مصادر التفسير]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>القران<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>السنة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>أقوال الصحابة<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ تَعَالَى:</span> <span class="c3">{وَالسَّمَاءِ وَالطَّارِقِ، وَمَا أَدْرَاكَ مَا الطَّارِقُ، النَّجْمُ الثَّاقِبُ}</span><a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>-<span class="c5"> قَال الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٣ص٤٥:</span> قَالَ ابْنُ عُيَيْنَةَ: <span class="c2">«مَا كَانَ فِي القُرْآنِ»</span> <span class="c3">{مَا أَدْرَاكَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الانفطار: ١٨]</span> <span class="c1">": فَقَدْ أَعْلَمَهُ، وَمَا قَالَ "</span>: <span class="c3">{وَمَا يُدْرِيكَ}</span> <span class="c4">[الأحزاب: ٦٣]</span> <span class="c1">": فَإِنَّهُ لَمْ يُعْلِمْهُ "</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>